reviews.text:
Photo and captions are not as food you will really get, and they insist not to change back as captions shown in menu, just said there’s only wording problems, insist not to change the food to the right item.

Fact is 
menu: Salmon Belly rice, 
actual food: Salmon SKIN? 
And staff and even CHEF who works there insist the SALMON SKIN is BELLY.

Thanks for the “great” catering experience.
Delicious food, cozy place, worth money value

Mid-priced Japanese restaurant serving the local residential community. It’s been opened for 4 years & proven to be well received by customers in neighborhood. We’re there at Tuesday night & still at least 70% of tables were taken, not bad at all. Sashimis were generally ok. I liked the best that night were grilled fresh goose intestines & miso-stewed fresh ox intestines 😋
nice Japanese restaurant, fresh sashimi

The food is nice, but that's all what I can say positive about my first visit in this restaurant. Staff seemed inexperienced, somewhat ignoring and not that customer oriented.
We got one set dinner and some sushi. On the set dinner there was something given to us which didn't belong there which we didn't notice. The staff returned and took it from the tray. Getting tea refill on demand, not very attentively I have to say. Some more smaller things I will leave out now.
Another thing is there are some sushi dinner sets, but the staff can't tell what's in. It's the chefs choice and it depends what he want to put. You really need to like all kinds of sushi for ordering that. If there is 1-2-3 you really don't like, then it's already a big part of the set.
I can go again, but just for the food and need to close my eyes of the rest.

鳥山名(愉景新城)

二人套餐幾抵食

今天想吃得簡單一些，又不要太多油膩的食物，選擇了「鳥山名」日本料理。他們的 $385 二人套餐份量好足夠，還有得選擇。首先是前菜拼盤，有水雲、生葵、八爪魚、明太子、漬物及慢煮牛舌，但今天牛舌缺貨，所以以赤貝沙律代替，各款有獨特口味，不錯。

溫泉玉子絹豆腐櫻花蝦沙律 清新爽口，麻醬配上溫泉玉子混合於新鮮沙律菜、小蕃茄及櫻花蝦，味道一流 非常嘢味，絹豆腐的豆香與幼滑，入口便可以感受到。

壽司盛盒有六件及卷物三件，有海蝦、魷魚、三文魚🍣、吞拿魚等，魚生的質素就比較一般。

小食我哋叫了芝士年糕及鹽燒三文魚腩骨，芝士年糕超正，年糕的外層一點也不感到油膩，內裏的芝士混合了年糕非常糯糥的 ，多來一粒也可以😂。

和食是鹽燒鯖魚，不要小看那塊鯖魚，它不但肥美、濃濃的魚香 還有很多肉汁，很好味。另外附上的燒菠蘿 很香甜 還能替大家清清口腔，刺激一下味蕾。

御飯 選了一碗珍珠飯和一個清湯烏冬，清湯烏冬附上甜腐豆及超甜粟米，烏冬打得很好有嚼口，我喜歡。珍珠飯就不太珍珠，米粒比較長身，不夠糯，少少失望。

好喜歡他們的甜品，黑芝麻椰子奶凍 好香滑，有質感。紅豆大大粒，甜美有豆香，配合奶凍超棒。
小心中伏餐牌所見嘅壽司完全唔同冇人提你， 二百幾蚊一個餐比三蚊店的出品還要差
午市來的， 食物質素不錯而且不貴，侍應們都好有禮貌， 如果一家大細的話也坐得舒服！假日2:15後下午茶時段有25%off,  好抵食！
在D.PARK 是不錯的日本料理。

reviews.text: Excellent place for family with kids. Can spend all day here with reasonable cost. Public facilities, shops and entertainment are all well designed with kids in mind. The cinema is even decorated and provided with kids seats and play areas. Coming place is more spacious than you could imagine.
Large mall with wide variety of shops, restaurants, and a cinema, but no supermarket. Great place for families with young kids. Parking is relatively cheap.
Good location, family friendly! Good for shopping with kids

A large and well designed shopping mall. Shops were of large types and properly located at different areas of the mall. Food choices were absurd with a bizarre choice from local fast food to American tastes to top-of-the-class cuisines. A huge recommendation for foodies. Activities there are also never-ending and makes the mall suitable for children and adults of all ages.
Spacious.  Good restaurants.  Convenient supermarket.  Comfortable weeknight visit.
